dc_title_s: Pleistocene Geology of Dane County, Wisconsin
dc_description_s: Description of the geologic history of Dane County. The preface points out the significance of glacial landscape research at WGNHS over the past century. Many pictures and diagrams and a four-color map and cross sections show the striking differences between glaciated and unglaciated regions of the county.
dct_provenance_s: Wisconsin Geological and Natural History Survey
dc_creator_sm: Wisconsin Geological and Natural History Survey
